************************************************************
STJERM:

* version SVN
* a terminal emulator which shows up and hides by pressing the
  shortcut key
* by Stjepan Glavina

************************************************************
REQUIREMENTS:

* mono
* gtk-sharp-2
* vte

************************************************************
SIMPLE INSTALLATION:

Compile:
    ./compile
Install (as root):
    ./install

Uninstall (as root):
	./uninstall

************************************************************
ADVANCED INSTALLATION:

Compile:
    ./compile
Install (as root):
    ./install
To install in a custom directory:
	./install /path/to/your/directory
Uninstall:
	./uninstall
If you installed Stjerm in a custom directory, you must specify that directory:
	./uninstall /path/to/your/directory

************************************************************
KNOWN BUGS:

No known bugs at the moment.
If you find any, please report them to stjepang AT gmail DOT com.

